1 Albus Dumbledore
Rare/Holo Character
Wizard/Unique
If you have at least 4 Lessons in play, your Spell cards
with a printed Power cost of 6 or more need 2 less Power to play. (You still
need at least 1 Power that matches.)
newcard
2 Argus Filch
Rare/Holo Character
Unique
You may use an Action to discard an Adventure from play
(yours or your opponent's). (You don't get the reward.)
newcard
3 Crabbe &amp; Goyle
Rare/Holo Character
Wizard/Slytherin/Unique
You may use an Action and discard 2 cards from your hand to
do 3 damage to your opponent.
newcard
4 Detention!
Rare/Foil Adventure
Effect: Your opponent can't use Actions to play Adventure
cards.
To Solve: Your opponent chooses 2 Adventure cards in his or
her hand and discards them.
Opponent's Reward: Your opponent may draw a card.
newcard
5 Dragon's Blood
Rare/Foil Spell
7P
To play this card, discard 2 of your P Lessons from play. Do
11 damage to your opponent or to a Creature of your choice.
newcard
6 Dumbledore's Watch
Rare/Foil Item
Unique
9T
If this card is in play before your turn, discard all cards
(other than each player's starting Character) from play (including this card).
newcard
7 End-of-Year Feast
Rare/Foil Spell
4C
Put up to 4 Adventure cards from your discard pile into your
hand.
newcard
8 Fang
Rare/Foil Creature/Dog
Unique
8F
To play this card, discard 1 of your F Lessons from play.
When you play this card, do 4 damage to your opponent.
Damage each turn: 4, Health: 7
newcard
9 Finding the Platform
Rare/Foil Adventure
Effect: Your opponent can't use Actions to play Location
cards.
To Solve: Your opponent lets you search your deck. You may
take up to 2 Location cards from your deck, show them to your opponent and put
them into your hand. Then shuffle your deck.
Opponent's Reward: Your opponent may put a Lesson card from
his or her hand into play.
newcard
10 Galleon
Rare/Foil Item/Money
10C
You can play only 1 Money card each turn. Before your turn,
if this card is in play, discard it and your get 3 more Actions this turn.
newcard
11 Great Hall
Rare/Foil Location
Unique
2C
When you play this card, discard any other Location from
play (yours or your opponent's). Before each player's turn, he or she draws a
card.
newcard
12 Hagrid's House
Rare/Foil Location
Unique
3F
When you play this card, discard any other Location from
play (yours or your opponent's). Whenever a F Lesson (yours or your opponent's)
is discarded from play, put it into its owner's hand.
newcard
13 Harry Triumphant
Rare/Holo Character
Wizard/Gryffindor/Unique
At the end of each of your turns, if you played an Adventure
card that turn, draw up to 4 cards.
newcard
14 Hospital Dormitory
Rare/Foil Location
7P
When you play this card, discard any other Location from
play (yours or your opponent's). Each turn, each player may prevent 4 damage
done to him or her. (The damage may be prevented from one or more cards.)
newcard
15 Hut on the Rock
Rare/Foil Adventure
Play this card only if you have at least 5 Lessons in play.
Effect: Before each of your opponent's turns, if he or she
has any cards in play (other than his or her starting Character), he or she
chooses 1 of them and discards it.
To Solve: Your opponent discards his or her hand.
Opponent's Reward: You take 5 damage.
newcard
16 Madam Pomfrey 
Rare/Holo Character
Witch/Unique/Healing
Once per game, you may shuffle up to 12 non-Healing cards
from your discard pile into your deck. 
newcard
17 Meeting Fluffy
Rare/Foil Adventure
Play this card only if you have at least 9 Lessons in play.
Effect: Before each of your turns, your opponent takes 12
damage.
To Solve: Your opponent lets you choose 3 of his or her
cards in play (other than his or her starting Character) and discard them.
Opponent's Reward: Your opponent gets 1 more Action the turn
he or she solves this Adventure.
newcard
18 Midnight Duel
Rare/Foil Adventure
Play this card only if you have at least 5 Lessons in play.
Effect: To use an Action to play a Creature or a Spell card
from his or her hand, your opponent must discard another card from his or her
hand.
To Solve: Your opponent chooses 4 of his or her cards in
play (other than his or her starting Character) and discards them.
Opponent's Reward: Your opponent may draw 4 cards.
newcard
19 Mirror of Erised
Rare/Foil Item
Unique
10T
You may use an Action to discard this card from play. If you
do, count the number of cards in your hand and discard them. Then search your
deck. You may take up to that number of cards from your deck and put them into
your hand. Then shuffle your deck.
newcard
20 Peeves
Rare/Holo Character
Unique
Once per game, you may discard your hands and draw 7 cards
to make your opponent discard his or her hand and then draw 7 cards.
newcard
21 Philosopher's Stone
Rare/Foil Item/Healing
Unique
15T
You may use 2 Actions to discard this card from play to put
all Lesson cards from your discard pile into play. Then shuffle all non-Healing
cards from your discard pile into your deck. When you build your deck, you can
only put 1 Philosopher's Stone in it.
newcard
22 Potions Dungeon
Rare/Foil Location
Unique
3P
