31 5 Points from Gryffindor
Uncommon Adventure
Play this card only if you have at least 5 Lessons in play.
Effect: Your opponent gets 1 fewer Action on each of his or
her turns (even the turn this Adventure is solved). (If this would mean your
opponent would have fewer than 1 Action, he or she still gets 1 Action.)
To Solve: Your opponent chooses 5 cards from his or her hand
and discards them.
Opponent's Reward: You take 5 damage.
newcard
